arts.ttl: Cheltenham Town v Barrow RECAP: Matty Taylor double sparks Robins fightback
arts.sum: Cheltenham Town: Day; Stubbs, Bennett (Hay 51), Bradbury; Jude-Boyd, Young, Archer, Adedokun; Thomas (Power 89), Miller (Taylor 51), Williams (Bakare 84). Matty Taylor scored twice as Cheltenham Town hit back from 2-0 down to claim a thrilling 3-2 victory over Barrow in League Two on Saturday.
